    - KERNEL32: o removed experimental heap handle cache stats

 2001-10-21: Sander van Leeuwen <sandervl@xs4all.nl>
    - WSOCK32:  o Fix for sending FD_CLOSE notification when connection
                  is closed at the remote end.

